data.description: This spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom house sits on just under 5 acres of pure tranquility. Surrounded by nature, this property offers a perfect blend of open space and privacy, making it an ideal haven for nature lovers and those seeking serenity. Step inside this charming home and be captivated by the generous living spaces. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and family time. The kitchen boasts ample storage, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual meals. A very spacious primary bedroom and bathroom, and the two additional bedrooms are also very spacious as well. But it's the outdoor space that truly sets this property apart. The land features a mix of open space and partially wooded areas, allowing for endless possibilities. It's a paradise for outdoor enthusiasts. The huge barn and shop on the property are perfect for hobbyists, artists, or those in need of ample storage space. Whether you dream of having a workshop, studio, or simply need a space for your tools and equipment, this versatile structure has got you covered. With its spacious interior, expansive land, and versatile barn and shop, this house is an opportunity not to be missed.  Your dream home awaits – come and experience it today! (NEW ROOF 9/23)
